Changelog automation

- Keep a changelog style for changes
- Use ``towncrier`` for changelog generation
- See docs for more info on how to `create newsfragments <https://fluiddyn.readthedocs.io/en/latest/mercurial_heptapod.html#documenting-the-merge-request-with-towncrier>`__ and `make releases <https://fluiddyn.readthedocs.io/en/latest/workflow_release.html>`__
